Feature: Confringo (Blasting Curse)

    Causes anything that the spell meets to explode in flames.

    Pronunciation:
        /kɒnˈfrɪŋɡoʊ/ kon-FRING-goh
    Seen/mentioned:
        Seen only in Deathly Hallows. In the opening chapters, it is cast by
        Harry to destroy the sidecar of the flying motorbike.[DH Ch.4] Later,
        it is used by Hermione in an attempt to kill Nagini and facilitate an
        escape from Bathilda Bagshot's house in Godric's Hollow.[DH Ch.17]
